  "text": "Held in 2003, the ICDAR 2003 Robust Reading Competition [CITATION_1] is the first such benchmark dataset that's ever released for scene text detection and recognitio.Among the 509 images, 258 are used for training and 251 for testing. The dataset is also used in ICDAR 2005 Text Locating Competition [CITATION_2] . ICDAR 2015 also includes a digit recognition track.",
